(2, 'jczxdb-fipjnz-purtif-vojuhg-tpyflq', '0', 'Newsletter', '2018-09-20 15:29:04', '2018-09-20 15:29:04', 1, '<strong style=\"color: #990000\">What can you achieve using Email Subscribers?</strong><p>Add subscription forms on website, send HTML newsletters & automatically notify subscribers about new blog posts once it is published. You can also Import or Export subscribers from any list to Email Subscribers.</p> <strong style=\"color: #990000\">Plugin Features</strong><ol> <li>Send notification emails to subscribers when new blog posts are published.</li> <li>Subscribe form available with 3 options to setup.</li> <li>Double Opt-In and Single Opt-In support.</li> <li>Email notification to admin when a new user signs up (Optional).</li> <li>Automatic welcome email to subscriber.</li> <li>Auto add unsubscribe link in the email.</li> <li>Import/Export subscriber emails to migrate to any lists.</li> <li>Default WordPress editor to create emails.</li> </ol> <strong>Thanks & Regards,</strong><br>Admin', 'Sent', 'Immediately', 'Welcome To Email Subscribers');
