;}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31539:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for a small business? For a small business website, you&#8217;ll need a theme that can showcase your products and services professionally. </p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress business themes for small businesses.</p>\n<h3>Making a Small Business Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the best website builder in the world. It&#8217;s easy to set up and flexible in terms of features. WordPress is used by many top brands for their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 types of WordPress on the market: WordPress.com is a hosted solution, whereas WordPress.org is a self-hosted platform. See our detailed comparison between <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\" title=\"WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org  Is One Really Better Than the Other?\">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for more information.</p>\n<p>To create a small business website, we recommend using self-hosted WordPress.org which is more powerful and offers instant access to all its features.</p>\n<p>First, you&#8217;ll need to buy a domain name and a web hosting account. Web hosting costs around $7.99 per month. Initially, this fee can feel like a lot for a small business website.</p>\n<p>We recommend using Bluehost web hosting. They&#8217;re an official WordPress hosting partner, and one of the top WordPress companies in the world.</p>\n<p>Plus, Bluehost is offering a free domain, SSL certificate, and a discount on web hosting to our readers. You can get all of it for $2.75 / month, which is much more reasonable for launching your small business website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bluehost-review.png\" alt=\"bluehost review\" width=\"370\" height=\"233\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221568\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bluehost-review.png 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/bluehost-review-300x189.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Once purchased, you can follow our complete guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)\">how to make a website</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-install-a-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"How to install a WordPress theme\">install a theme in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, take a look at the best WordPress themes for small business websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/2237-2/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Enterprise Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/2237-2/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Enterprise Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enterprise.jpg\" alt=\"Enterprise\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221701\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enterprise.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enterprise-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enterprise-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Enterprise pro is a beautiful WordPress theme built specifically for small business and corporate websites. It&#8217;s based on the Genesis theme framework, which gives the theme a rock solid foundation. Enterprise Pro comes with built-in sections to display your services, featured content, team profiles, and more.</p>\n<p>It ships with a full-width navigation menu, custom image slider, and unlimited color schemes. You can use the live customizer to edit the theme and add your content quickly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Landing\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Landing</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-landing/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Landing\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/landing-1.jpg\" alt=\"Landing\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221628\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/landing-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/landing-1-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/landing-1-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Landing is an excellent WordPress theme that can be adapted easily for your small business website. It offers a built-in <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)\">page builder</a> which helps you quickly create pages and launch your website.</p>\n<p>It features ready-made page templates, full-width background sliders, parallax effects, header templates, and a lot more. Landing is easy to set up and offers premium features for small business websites.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-executive-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Executive Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Executive Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-executive-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Executive Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/executivepro.jpg\" alt=\"Executive Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222025\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/executivepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/executivepro-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/executivepro-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Executive Pro is a stunning WordPress theme for small business, corporate, or professional services websites. It&#8217;s built on the Genesis framework and uses a built-in page builder to add features. The theme includes ready-made page templates, newsletter subscription forms, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">contact form</a> support, and more.</p>\n<p>It offers a fullscreen image slider with a call-to-action button. It has unlimited color options, widget-ready layouts, custom theme options, and a powerful navigation menu.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Float</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-float/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Float\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/float.jpg\" alt=\"Float\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221630\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/float.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/float-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/float-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Float is a powerful WordPress theme designed specifically for small business websites. It comes with a ready-to-use page builder to quickly launch your website.</p>\n<p>It includes page templates, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/\" title=\"12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)\">social media</a> icons, infinite color schemes, parallax effects, beautiful background options, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ultra-1.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221627\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ultra-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ultra-1-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ultra-1-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ultra is a perfect WordPress theme for small business websites. It has built-in layouts that can be used to create a website of your choice in no time. You can use the powerful page builder to add features and content on your website.</p>\n<p>Other notable features include multiple navigation menus, custom widgets, unlimited color schemes, custom theme options panel, and a whole lot more. Ultra is fully optimized for <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/wordpress-performance-speed/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Ultimate Guide to Boost WordPress Speed &#038; Performance\">speed and performance</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/brooklyn/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Brooklyn\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Brooklyn</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/brooklyn/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"The Advisors\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/brooklyn-wordpress-theme-review-1024x514.png\" alt=\"Brooklyn WordPress Theme Review\" width=\"1024\" height=\"514\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1680\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/brooklyn-wordpress-theme-review-1024x514.png 1024w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/brooklyn-wordpress-theme-review-300x150.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/brooklyn-wordpress-theme-review-768x385.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Brooklyn is one of the best WordPress business themes available in the ThemeForest marketplace. Its trusted by over 30,000 customers worldwide and is among the top 3 bestselling creative themes of all time. </p>\n<p>Brooklyn comes with 30+ premade WordPress demos that can be installed with just a click. Its powerful admin panel has a huge menu of design options. The theme comes bundled with 2 premium plugins: Revolution Slider and Visual Composer. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Presence</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-presence/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Presence\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/presence.jpg\" alt=\"Presence\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222027\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/presence.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/presence-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/presence-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Presence is a modern and professional WordPress theme for small business websites. It can be used on multiple business niches like real-estate, hotels, restaurants, music, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and offers demos to quickly launch your website.</p>\n<p>It features ready-made website sections for team members, about, portfolio, services, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hermesthemes-prestige/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Best Testimonial Plugins for WordPress\">testimonials</a>, and a contact form. Presence theme works great with all third-party page builders for easy customization.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Roxima</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-roxima/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Roxima\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/roxima.jpg\" alt=\"Roxima\" width=\"775\" height=\"385\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221679\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/roxima.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/roxima-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/roxima-768x382.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Roxima is a stylish WordPress theme with premium features for your small business and corporate websites. It offers custom theme options, multiple page layouts, widget-ready areas, and more.</p>\n<p>It comes with ready-made homepage sections for clients, portfolio, products, services, and team members. You can use the live theme customizer to quickly set up your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/vantage/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vantage\" rel=\"nofollow\">9. Vantage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/vantage/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vantage\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/vantage.jpg\" alt=\"Vantage\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222028\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/vantage.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/vantage-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/vantage-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Vantage is a free WordPress theme with amazing features to design a small business website. It fully supports Site Origin&#8217;s page builder plugin for quick setup and easy customization.</p>\n<p>It comes with custom page layouts, color options, companion plugins, and more. You can use the page builder to create your own layouts and templates.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">10. Hestia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hestia.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221698\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hestia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hestia-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hestia-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hestia Pro is a beautiful and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-multi-purpose-themes/\" title=\"22 Best WordPress Multi-Purpose Themes (2018)\">multi-purpose WordPress theme</a> that can be easily used to create small business websites. The homepage is fully widgetized, so you can drag and drop features to quickly set up and customize your website.</p>\n<p>It features a parallax background, custom widgets, image sliders, social media icons, and color options. It&#8217;s a highly customizable theme with premium features for your small business website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-advent/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Advent\" rel=\"nofollow\">11. Advent</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-advent/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Advent\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/advent.jpg\" alt=\"Advent\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222029\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/advent.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/advent-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/advent-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Advent is an elegant WordPress theme for small business and corporate websites. It can also be used as a landing page theme for your apps. Advent is fully customizable and offers homepage sections for overview, about, reviews, testimonials, and a portfolio.</p>\n<p>The homepage is widget-ready, which means you can easily drag and drop features. It supports custom widgets, image slider, navigation menus, header image, and more. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-creativo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Creativo\" rel=\"nofollow\">12. Creativo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-creativo/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Creativo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/creativo.jpg\" alt=\"Creativo\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222030\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/creativo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/creativo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/creativo-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Creativo is a WordPress theme for creative businesses. It offers multiple page layouts, theme skins, header templates, color options, and parallax backgrounds.</p>\n<p>It fully supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a>, so you can <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Create an Online Store in 2018  Step by Step (with Pictures)\">start an online store</a> easily. It also includes a drag and drop page builder, companion plugin for a live chat feature, portfolio content type, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-potenza/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Potenza\" rel=\"nofollow\">13. Potenza</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-potenza/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Potenza\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/potenza.jpg\" alt=\"Potenza\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222031\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/potenza.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/potenza-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/potenza-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Potenza is a WordPress business theme for small business and corporate websites. It offers premium features to design your homepage using a built-in page builder. The custom homepage slider allows you to showcase your featured posts and pages.</p>\n<p>In addition, it has custom widgets, page layouts, color options, powerful theme settings, and a lot more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-amaryllis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Amaryllis\" rel=\"nofollow\">14. Amaryllis</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-amaryllis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Amaryllis\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/amaryllis.jpg\" alt=\"Amaryllis\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222032\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/amaryllis.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/amaryllis-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/amaryllis-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Amaryllis is a beautiful WordPress theme for small eCommerce businesses. It supports WooCommerce out of the box, which means you can create an online store easily. Amaryllis features crisp typography, a large header image, a products section, and more.</p>\n<p>It includes a widget-based layout for the homepage, so you can simply drag and drop features. It&#8217;s fully optimized and easy to set up.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/screenr/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenr\" rel=\"nofollow\">15. Screenr</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/screenr/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Screenr\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/screenr.jpg\" alt=\"Screenr\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222033\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/screenr.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/screenr-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/screenr-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Screenr is a free WordPress business theme for small business websites. It features multiple header templates, a widget-ready hompeage, and parallax effects.</p>\n<p>It has custom widgets, page layouts, color options, and more. It&#8217;s a simple and easy-to-use WordPress theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-moesia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moesia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">16. Moesia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-moesia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Moesia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/moesiapro.jpg\" alt=\"Moesia Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"397\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221677\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/moesiapro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/moesiapro-300x154.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/moesiapro-768x393.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Moesia is a stylish WordPress theme designed specifically for small business websites. It&#8217;s packed with a full-width background image on the homepage. You can add text and a call-to-action button on the image.</p>\n<p>It includes a powerful page builder that can be used to create your own custom layouts for the homepage and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)\">landing pages</a>. It supports Google Fonts, multiple sliders, sidebars, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-ampersand/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ampersand\" rel=\"nofollow\">17. Ampersand</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-ampersand/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ampersand\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ampersand.jpg\" alt=\"Ampersand\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221670\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ampersand.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ampersand-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/ampersand-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you are looking for a simple-yet-modern WordPress theme, then Ampersand is the right choice. It comes with a two-column layout, multiple featured content sections, header image, and more.</p>\n<p>It offers custom page layouts, a separate blog page, landing pages templates, and other useful premium features for your small business website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/make/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Make\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Make</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/make/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Make\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/make.jpg\" alt=\"Make\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222034\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/make.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/make-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/make-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Make is another free WordPress theme for your small business website. It features a built-in page builder that can be used to create your own layout.</p>\n<p>It includes multiple ready-to-use templates to launch your website quickly. Make is easy to set up and works great with all <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Plugins that You MUST Use (2018)\">third-party WordPress plugins</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-birch/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Birch\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Birch</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojo-marketplace-birch/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Birch\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/birch.jpg\" alt=\"Birch\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222035\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/birch.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/birch-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/birch-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Birch is a modern WordPress business theme with the perfect premium features for your small business website. It ships with beautiful typography, custom logo, image slider, and beautiful navigation menu.</p>\n<p>It also includes multiple built-in sections on the homepage for clients, portfolio, testimonials, services, and more. You can use the live customizer to edit and set up your theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-digital-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Digital Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. Digital Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-digital-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Digital Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/digitalprotheme.jpg\" alt=\"Digital Pro\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222036\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/digitalprotheme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/digitalprotheme-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/digitalprotheme-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Digital Pro is a WordPress theme for small digital businesses, media agencies, and corporate offices. It&#8217;s built on top of the Genesis framework, and offers useful features like a fullscreen header image on the homepage with text and a call-to-action button.</p>\n<p>It comes with custom widgets, color choices, navigation menus, page layouts, and a theme options panel for easy customization.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-struct/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Struct\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Struct</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-struct/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Struct\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/struct.jpg\" alt=\"Struct\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222037\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/struct.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/struct-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/struct-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Struct is a stunning WordPress theme for small businesses, start ups, and digital agencies. It ships with a drag and drop page builder, fully widget-based homepage, and more.</p>\n<p>Aside from that, it also includes ready-made sections on the homepage to showcase your portfolio, services, FAQs, testimonials, and services professionally.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/pinnacle/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pinnacle\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Pinnacle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/pinnacle/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pinnacle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/pinnacle.jpg\" alt=\"Pinnacle\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222038\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/pinnacle.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/pinnacle-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/pinnacle-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Pinnacle is a simple and free WordPress business theme suitable for your small business and corporate websites. It has a flat template, custom layouts, and beautiful design.</p>\n<p>The theme fully supports WooCommerce, and Google fonts for crisp typography.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/telsathemes-narcos/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Narcos\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Narcos</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/telsathemes-narcos/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Narcos\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/narcostheme.jpg\" alt=\"Narcos\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222040\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/narcostheme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/narcostheme-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/narcostheme-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Narcos is a modern and professional WordPress theme for all kinds of business websites. It has many premium features for your small business website, including parallax effects on the homepage, full-width header image, widget-based layout, and custom page templates.</p>\n<p>It also includes homepage sections for testimonials, team members, about, portfolio, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and can be customized using the live theme customizer.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-venture/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Venture\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Venture</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-venture/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Venture\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/venture.jpg\" alt=\"Venture\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222041\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/venture.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/venture-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/venture-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Venture is an excellent WordPress theme suitable for small businesses. It has a drag and drop page builder to quickly launch your website. The homepage is widget-based which makes it easy to add features and content.</p>\n<p>Venture fully supports WooCommerce. Other notable features include homepage slider, custom logo, navigation menus, color schemes, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-angle/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Angle\" rel=\"nofollow\">25. Angle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-angle/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Angle\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/angle-1.jpg\" alt=\"Angle\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222042\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/angle-1.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/angle-1-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/angle-1-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Angle is a premium WordPress business theme designed specifically for small business websites. It comes with a built-in drag and drop page builder that can be used to add features and content quickly. </p>\n<p>It has built-in sections for testimonials, portfolio, clients, about, contact, and more. Angle has multiple layouts to easily create your landing pages.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best WordPress business themes for small businesses. You may also want to see our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\" title=\"30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018\">how to make money from online blogging</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-business-themes/\">25 Best WordPress Business Themes for Your Website (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-business-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"How to Fix the Error Establishing a Database Connection in WordPress (Step by Step)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:86:\"https://www.isitwp.com/fix-error-establishing