I</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Toppings</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What is ramen without good toppings? Usually, they use soft-boiled egg, pork slices, bamboo shoots and chopped leeks. These toppings are not only for an instagramable visual. It is also to add flavor and extra kick to complete a killer ramen.</span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The word ramen sounds very simple but in contrary, it is a bowl of complex flavors and textures. As Erwan said, you either love a ramen or hate it. Youll love it because of the feeling you get when you eat it and probably hate it because its too perfect to be true. Love it or hate it, a good bowl of killer ramen will always be worth it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</span>', 'Erwan Heussaffs Anatomy of a Killer Ramen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '275-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-17 14:19:03', '2018-09-17 14:19:03', '', 275, 'http://page5.ph/275-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(280, 3, '2018-09-17 14:49:38', '2018-09-17 14:49:38', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Once again, E! gathers todays top social media influencers for a night of class and elegance. Annually, E! organizes a night where influential bloggers, vloggers, and social media influencers of the countrys digital community are recognized for their achievements and contributions  as usual, they never fail to surprise us with fresh concepts and ideas that makes us engrossed in such an event.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This year, E! is adding several new categories in recognition of the most trending influencers, the breakthrough social media stars, and the individuals who have become icons in the field of Beauty and Fashion, Food and Travel.  </span><b>E!</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lets have a look at these 4 things to look forward to on this years E! Bloggers Ball:</span>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><b>THE NOMINEES</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/vote\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/vote</span></a>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These amazing nominees were hand-picked by 9 respected members of the Blogger Council  each of whom are standing out as individuals, creating different contents but are driven with the same passion and drive to give us the best entertainment. </span>\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li><b>THE HOSTS</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/</span></a>\r\n\r\n<b> </b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Just by looking at these E! Bloggers Ball 2018 hosts, you already want to stay tuned with their Instagram stories and posts! Raymond Gutierrez, Nicole Andersson, and Janeena Chan are all known for their knack for hosting perfectly. With the three of them combined, we expect the night to be fun, exciting, and grand. E! sure knows how to combine the best trio!</span>\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li><b>OUTFIT INSPOS</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Who wouldnt want to cop their favorite influencers outfit of the night? Not you, for sure! With High Shine Fashion as this years theme, we all expect them to be glammed up with their own version of formal attires. Not only that, we will get to witness these icons play with todays outfit trends. Who do you think will be awarded as best dressed?</span>\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li><b>THE WINNERS</b></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With our all-out support to our favorite influencers, it is but normal to rave about who should get the awards for the night. E! mentioned that they added several new categories, and we cant wait to know who the winners are. The following awards are: E! Breakthrough Influencer of the Year. E! Look Whos Trending, E! Food Icon of the Year, E! Travel Icon of the Year, E! Beauty Icon of the Year, E! Fashion Icon of the Year, Best Dressed of the Night (Male), and Best Dressed of the Night (Female).</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Being an influencer is not a walk in the park. Oftentimes, they get envied by netizens for having such privileges and fame. Little do we know, all of them work hard to give us more than what we deserve. Some may even receive hate, but that doesnt give them the reason to stop hustling  spending exhausting nights editing their contents, and days filming and meeting with people. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In each E! Bloggers Ball, these influencers hard work and passion are recognized. They are given a night to celebrate their success and grow closer with people who share the same drive and passion. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Which influencer are you looking forward to spy on this coming E! Bloggers Ball 2018? Have you voted for your favorite influencer yet? Cast your votes now!</span>', 'E! Bloggers Ball 2018', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'e-bloggers-ball-2018__trashed', '', '', '2018-09-18 16:21:41', '2018-09-18 16:21:41', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=280', 0, 'post', '', 0),
