(285, 2, '2018-09-18 15:15:14', '2018-09-18 15:15:14', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In just a year, Alex Gonzaga has managed to take and prove her spot in the online sphere as she was named as this years Most Influential Female Social Media Personality in the Alta Media Icon Awards.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alex started vlogging in 2017 and continues to create hilarious and goofy contents with her sister Toni, mommy Pinty, boyfriend Mikee Morada, and other friends from showbiz and personal life.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Just recently, she threw a free-for-all concert to celebrate the first anniversary of her vlog.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Awards night is happening on October 5, 2018 at the University of Perpetual Help-Las Pinas.</span></p>', 'Alex hailed as Most Influential in Social Media', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'alex-hailed-as-most-influential-in-social-media', '', '', '2018-09-19 16:00:58', '2018-09-19 16:00:58', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=285', 0, 'post', '', 0),
