(292, 2, '2018-09-16 16:00:52', '2018-09-16 16:00:52', '<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Once again, E! gathers todays top social media influencers for a night of class and elegance. Annually, E! organizes a night where influential bloggers, vloggers, and social media influencers of the countrys digital community are recognized for their achievements and contributions  as usual, they never fail to surprise us with fresh concepts and ideas that makes us engrossed in such an event.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c5\">This year, E! is adding several new categories in recognition of the most trending influencers, the breakthrough social media stars, and the individuals who have become icons in the field of Beauty and Fashion, Food and Travel. </span><span class=\"c5 c12 c13\">E!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Lets have a look at these 4 things to look forward to on this years E! Bloggers Ball:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">1.</span><span class=\"c3\">THE NOMINEES</span></span></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-317 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/file-1-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-319 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/file2-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-318 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/file-3-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a href=\"https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/vote\">https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/vote</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">These amazing nominees were hand-picked by 9 respected members of the Blogger Council  each of whom are standing out as individuals, creating different contents but are driven with the same passion and drive to give us the best entertainment.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">2.</span><span class=\"c3\">THE HOSTS</span></span></h5>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-322 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/BLOGGERS-BALL-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/</span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Just by looking at these E! Bloggers Ball 2018 hosts, you already want to stay tuned with their Instagram stories and posts! Raymond Gutierrez, Nicole Andersson, and Janeena Chan are all known for their knack for hosting perfectly. With the three of them combined, we expect the night to be fun, exciting, and grand. E! sure knows how to combine the best trio!</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">3.</span><span class=\"c3\">OUTFIT INSPOS</span></span></h5>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\">Who wouldnt want to cop their favorite influencers outfit of the night? Not you, for sure! With High Shine Fashion as this years theme, we all expect them to be glammed up with their own version of formal attires. Not only that, we will get to witness these icons play with todays outfit trends. Who do you think will be awarded as best dressed?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-323 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/raiza-1-1024x655.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"409\" /> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-324 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/angel-1-1024x655.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"409\" /></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">4.</span><span class=\"c3\">THE WINNERS</span></span></h5>\r\n<p class=\"c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">With our all-out support to our favorite influencers, it is but normal to rave about who should get the awards for the night. E! mentioned that they added several new categories, and we cant wait to know who the winners are. The following awards are: E! Breakthrough Influencer of the Year. E! Look Whos Trending, E! Food Icon of the Year, E! Travel Icon of the Year, E! Beauty Icon of the Year, E! Fashion Icon of the Year, Best Dressed of the Night (Male), and Best Dressed of the Night (Female).</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-320 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/lloyd-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Being an influencer is not a walk in the park. Oftentimes, they get envied by netizens for having such privileges and fame. Little do we know, all of them work hard to give us more than what we deserve. Some may even receive hate, but that doesnt give them the reason to stop hustling  spending exhausting nights editing their contents, and days filming and meeting with people.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">In each E! Bloggers Ball, these influencers hard work and passion are recognized. They are given a night to celebrate their success and grow closer with people who share the same drive and passion.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Which influencer are you looking forward to spy on this coming E! Bloggers Ball 2018? Have you voted for your favorite influencer yet? Cast your votes now!</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'What to Expect in this year\'s E! Bloggers Ball 2018', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-to-expect-in-this-years-e-bloggers-ball-2018', '', '', '2018-09-22 20:11:16', '2018-09-22 20:11:16', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=292', 0, 'post', '', 0),
