;\">These amazing nominees were hand-picked by 9 respected members of the Blogger Council  each of whom are standing out as individuals, creating different contents but are driven with the same passion and drive to give us the best entertainment.</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">2.</span><span class=\"c3\">THE HOSTS</span></span></h5>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-322 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/BLOGGERS-BALL-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">https://www.clozette.co/ebloggersballph/</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Just by looking at these E! Bloggers Ball 2018 hosts, you already want to stay tuned with their Instagram stories and posts! Raymond Gutierrez, Nicole Andersson, and Janeena Chan are all known for their knack for hosting perfectly. With the three of them combined, we expect the night to be fun, exciting, and grand. E! sure knows how to combine the best trio!</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h5 class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"c7\">3.</span><span class=\"c3\">OUTFIT INSPOS</span></span></h5>\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\">Who wouldnt want to cop their favorite influencers outfit of the night? Not you, for sure! With High Shine Fashion as this years theme, we all expect them to be glammed up with their own version of formal attires. Not only that, we will get to witness these icons play with todays outfit trends. Who do you think will be awarded as best dressed?</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-323 size-large\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/raiza-1-1024x655.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"409\" /> <img class=\"alignnone 