(389, 2, '2018-09-19 14:34:39', '2018-09-19 14:34:39', '<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Its been over a month since school started and parents are probably stressed about one of the most important parts of their childs school life  snack time! It is very frustrating and challenging especially when kids are very picky and ignore the food you prepare. Here, Andi Manzano shares 3 of Olivias favorite healthy snacks kids can enjoy at school or even at home.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">The first snack box full of food consists of cookies, raisins, apples and cheese sandwich cut in squares. Andi uses the Cheez Whiz Mild which Olivia really enjoys. It has a cheesy milky taste kids will surely love as well. Also, Olivia likes to spread her Cheez Whiz on her bread by herself and Andi fries it on a pan with butter and flattens it. This combination of healthy snacks really is healthy and satisfying.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\nImage courtesy of Andi Manzano https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe second one is kind of smaller and usually includes fruits and cereals. Here, she puts grapes cut in two and star-shaped cereals.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Andi Manzanos Top 3 Healthy Snacks to Add on your Kids Snack Box', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '328-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 14:34:39', '2018-09-19 14:34:39', '', 328, 'http://page5.ph/328-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(390, 2, '2018-09-19 14:35:19', '2018-09-19 14:35:19', '<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Its been over a month since school started and parents are probably stressed about one of the most important parts of their childs school life  snack time! It is very frustrating and challenging especially when kids are very picky and ignore the food you prepare. Here, Andi Manzano shares 3 of Olivias favorite healthy snacks kids can enjoy at school or even at home.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">The first snack box full of food consists of cookies, raisins, apples and cheese sandwich cut in squares. Andi uses the Cheez Whiz Mild which Olivia really enjoys. It has a cheesy milky taste kids will surely love as well. Also, Olivia likes to spread her Cheez Whiz on her bread by herself and Andi fries it on a pan with butter and flattens it. This combination of healthy snacks really is healthy and satisfying.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n<h6>Image courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a></h6>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe second one is kind of smaller and usually includes fruits and cereals. Here, she puts grapes cut in two and star-shaped cereals.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Andi Manzanos Top 3 Healthy Snacks to Add on your Kids Snack Box', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '328-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 14:35:19', '2018-09-19 14:35:19', '', 328, 'http://page5.ph/328-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(391, 2, '2018-09-19 14:38:39', '2018-09-19 14:38:39', '<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Its been over a month since school started and parents are probably stressed about one of the most important parts of their childs school life  snack time! It is very frustrating and challenging especially when kids are very picky and ignore the food you prepare. Here, Andi Manzano shares 3 of Olivias favorite healthy snacks kids can enjoy at school or even at home.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">The first snack box full of food consists of cookies, raisins, apples and cheese sandwich cut in squares. Andi uses the Cheez Whiz Mild which Olivia really enjoys. It has a cheesy milky taste kids will surely love as well. Also, Olivia likes to spread her Cheez Whiz on her bread by herself and Andi fries it on a pan with butter and flattens it. This combination of healthy snacks really is healthy and satisfying.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\nImage courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe second one is kind of smaller and usually includes fruits and cereals. Here, she puts grapes cut in two and star-shaped cereals.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\nImage courtesy of Andi Manzano https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe last snack box consists one of Olivias favorite foods  MAC AND CHEESE! Not only does she have it for snack, she also enjoys it at lunch and dinner. This mouth-watering food is probably most of kids favorite go-to food. Andi uses the original Cheez Whiz and adds milk for a cheesy yummy snack. To add an extra kick to this menu, Andi adds corn which Olivia enjoys along with grapes and chocolate wafer.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-335\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\nImage courtesy of Andi Manzano https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAs a new mom, Andi makes sure to give her daughter healthy snacks and likes to prepare it herself with the help of Olivia. Not only does it make Olivia learn how to make her own snacks, it also gives her and Andi an enjoyable and knowledgeable way to bond with each other. While a child is learning, give them memories to cherish because they can only be a child once in their lives.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-333\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-330\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Andi Manzanos Top 3 Healthy Snacks to Add on your Kids Snack Box', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '328-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 14:38:39', '2018-09-19 14:38:39', '', 328, 'http://page5.ph/328-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
