(393, 2, '2018-09-19 14:40:34', '2018-09-19 14:40:34', '<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Its been over a month since school started and parents are probably stressed about one of the most important parts of their childs school life  snack time! It is very frustrating and challenging especially when kids are very picky and ignore the food you prepare. Here, Andi Manzano shares 3 of Olivias favorite healthy snacks kids can enjoy at school or even at home.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">The first snack box full of food consists of cookies, raisins, apples and cheese sandwich cut in squares. Andi uses the Cheez Whiz Mild which Olivia really enjoys. It has a cheesy milky taste kids will surely love as well. Also, Olivia likes to spread her Cheez Whiz on her bread by herself and Andi fries it on a pan with butter and flattens it. This combination of healthy snacks really is healthy and satisfying.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The second one is kind of smaller and usually includes fruits and cereals. Here, she puts grapes cut in two and star-shaped cereals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p