(397, 2, '2018-09-19 14:47:40', '2018-09-19 14:47:40', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In just a year, Alex Gonzaga has managed to take and prove her spot in the online sphere as she was named as this years Most Influential Female Social Media Personality in the Alta Media Icon Awards.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Alex started vlogging in 2017 and continues to create hilarious and goofy contents with her sister Toni, mommy Pinty, boyfriend Mikee Morada, and other friends from showbiz and personal life.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Just recently, she threw a free-for-all concert to celebrate the first anniversary of her vlog.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Awards night is happening on October 5, 2018 at the University of Perpetual Help-Las Pinas.</span></p>', 'Alex hailed as Most Influential in Social Media', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '285-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 14:47:40', '2018-09-19 14:47:40', '', 285, 'http://page5.ph/285-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(398, 2, '2018-09-20 15:04:42', '2018-09-20 15:04:42', '<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Filipina Cosplayer Alodia Gosiengfia is expected to attend this years French Championship of Cosplay after she was announced as one of the main judges of the competition.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Alodia shared the good news with excitement via her Facebook fan page:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-400\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Capture.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"449\" height=\"394\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c9\">So thrilled to be at</span><span class=\"c12 c14\"><a class=\"c13\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/comicconparis/?fref%3Dmentions%26__xts__%255B0%255D%3D68.ARB_7lWKkti9MEgV5C4oVFdPLQH79wBpvHLoH_W3pFGbRtnGdQE3Unae6Ju94PWD-B9dfDUyTY8PhpzEtbw3R0rb5RKv5W2b2WwzDNAsOCj0cQPSdJMPqfFnTsMYx2HuOBXq1-JRe2U9W6Ja3zQOe4OZDxQEz6wLmWq8hINH6Wf-qiQjT87epnU%26__tn__%3DK-R&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1537372219880000\">Comic Con Paris</a></span><span class=\"c9\">this October!</span><span class=\"c3\"></span><span class=\"c9\">Will be joining the panel of judges in The French Championships 2018 ! Really looking forward to meeting people in the community there as well!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Her influence and credibility for cosplaying various different cartoon characters and video games can be traced back in 2003 when she won the title for C3 Convention with her character of Rikku from Final Fantasy X-2.</p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c1\">Alodia will also be joined by other prominent personalities in the industry such as Eulyn Colette Hufkie, costume designer for The Walking Dead series, Arlek1 who was hailed as the grand winner of the festivals 2017 Edition, Capjux, Lily On the Moon, Han Jones among others.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Proclaimed winner of the said competition will be sent to Chicago and represent France during the world finals of the C2E2 Championship (Chicago Comic &amp; Enternaiment Expo).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Comic Con Paris will take place on October 26-28, 2018 at Grande Halle de la Villette 75019 Paris.</p>\r\n&nbsp;', '#PinoyPride: Alodia to judge at Comic Con Paris 2018', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pinoypride-alodia-to-judge-at-comic-con-paris-2018', '', '', '2018-09-22 20:13:40', '2018-09-22 20:13:40', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=398', 0, 'post', '', 0),
