(422, 2, '2018-09-19 15:37:55', '2018-09-19 15:37:55', '<p class=\"c0 c4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">A killer ramen is what most of us look for. A rich and tasty broth with perfectly cooked noodles and high quality toppings. A bowl overflowing with flavors, colors and textures. Not to forget, the feeling of satisfaction and warmth with every slurp of a hearty bowl of magic. Ramen has that addicting allure no one could ever possibly resist.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0 c4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">These days, the popularity of ramen noodles seems to keep growing. Ramen houses are popping everywhere, giving us all the kinds of good.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-409\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-11-19-13-16-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff <a href=\"https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI\">https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0 c4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">Erwan Heussaff, living the dreams of ramen lovers, went to search for the best ramen in Manila and shared what a bowl of ramen should have. Erwan tried various types of ramen such as Shoyu Ramen, Cheese Tantanmen and Shiromaru Special from the top 3 famous ramen houses in Manila. Join him as he dissects a bowl of a killer and soul-warming ramen.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"c0 c4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">1.Broth</span></h5>\r\n<p class=\"c0 c6\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">The broth is the star of the ramen, Erwan said. It depends on the type of ramen you want. It varies from thick to thin and rich to not-so-rich.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-411\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-11-19-18-05-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0 c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff <a href=\"https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI\">https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</a></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"c0 c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">2.Noodles</span></h5>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">The noodles are obviously the filling ones in a bowl of ramen. You can have it the way you want whether it is soft or firm or anything in between. Either way, it wont alter the magnificent taste of the ramen.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-413\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-11-19-19-07-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0 c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI\"> https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</a></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"c0 c8\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">3.Toppings</span></h5>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c18\">What is ramen without good toppings? Usually, they use soft-boiled egg, pork slices, bamboo shoots and chopped leeks. These toppings are not only for an instagramable visual. It is also to add flavor and extra kick to complete a killer ramen.</span><span class=\"c13\"></span><span class=\"c2\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-410\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-11-19-17-36-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff <a href=\"https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI\">https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</a></span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"c0 c4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c2\">The word ramen sounds very simple but in contrary, it is a bowl of complex flavors and textures. As Erwan said, you either love a ramen or hate it. Youll love it because of the feeling you get when you eat it and probably hate it because its too perfect to be true.Love it or hate it, a good bowl of killer ramen will always be worth it.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-412\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-11-19-18-20-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"c7\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Erwan Heussaff <a href=\"https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI\">https://youtu.be/vX06YZ6M0VI</a></span></p>', 'Erwan Heussaffs Anatomy of a Killer Ramen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '408-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 15:37:55', '2018-09-19 15:37:55', '', 408, 'http://page5.ph/408-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
