njoys it at lunch and dinner. This mouth-watering food is probably most of kids favorite go-to food. Andi uses the original Cheez Whiz and adds milk for a cheesy yummy snack. To add an extra kick to this menu, Andi adds corn which Olivia enjoys along with grapes and chocolate wafer.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-335\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a></span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a new mom, Andi makes sure to give her daughter healthy snacks and likes to prepare it herself with the help of Olivia. Not only does it make Olivia learn how to make her own snacks, it also gives her and Andi an enjoyable and knowledgeable way to bond with each other. While a child is learning, give them memories to cherish because they can only be a child once in their lives.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-333\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-330\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/andi-image6.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"c6\">Image courtesy of Andi Manzano <a href=\"https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI\">https://youtu.be/fnMb3nNAPUI</a></span><span class=\"c3\"></span></span>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>', 'Andi Manzanos Top 3 Healthy Snacks to Add on your Kids Snack Box', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '328-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-19 16:10:12', '2018-09-19 16:10:12', '', 328, 'http://page5.ph/328-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
