 channel.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-447\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-20-21-34-03-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Image courtesy of Raiza Contawi https://youtu.be/9JG6U1jrdLo</span></p>\r\n<p id=\"h.gjdgxs\" class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Also, Raf Juane already has a challenge of wearing Mac Cosmetics for 8 hours in his channel. Of course, one of those products is Maines lipstick.</span><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-448\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-20-21-47-17-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Image courtesy of About Raf https://youtu.be/eJayaClpybQ</span></p>\r\n<p id=\"h.gjdgxs-1\" class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c9\">Everyone must have their hands itch with eagerness. The most awaited limited-edition lippie will be out on September 21 in Lazada, 22 in Megamall and 23 in all MAC stores nationwide! Whos excited?</span></p>', '#MacForMaine Attended By Beauty Vloggers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '438-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-21 19:09:31', '2018-09-21 19:09:31', '', 438, 'http://page5.ph/438-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
