(476, 2, '2018-09-11 20:02:44', '2018-09-11 20:02:44', '<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Recently, an online couple named Jamill became the latest loveteam making noise in the social media. Jayzam Manabat and Camille Trinidad or Jamill has become one of the youtube couple vloggers netizens have been following.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/CPHCiRjNSHf9l6Hid_ludYNttuTR5JCpbDfJSJAL9CasItz6PrpBmYhiW15oAE_LeGxKh-YHGKAdeTKqlQ91K3mxtCJFC5KhMtbu4jwMdsSTTZzsc9VLR645q_N4Q6S0m2hsh3sl\" alt=\"\" /><span class=\"c0\">\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BluxUXIl64T/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=xmp6xwfi2w36</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">From their funny pranks to cute absurd moments, they captured the hearts of their fans easily. With their unique video contents and kilig factor, they are able to make their own name famous among other famous youtubers. Jamill really knows how to please their fans.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/id1Q_rDsX-x--bApqeXZcLBxF1OByNQls486JhCe239fBaa00b3Pe-XgTXckJ6X3JbLChD6JJ9L89y3jWEwItZRK2poXdwlGz6bgT42EOzWLDzkU7SCXKmuBFeP8BZwCRsQ2NQBS\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BjfCkfYlLTz/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=15z64d3o1gads</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">\r\nA car without a gasoline cant move forward to its destination. Just like how every idol needs its fandom. Without the netizens, an idol wouldnt be where he/she is now. We can not deny the fact that Jamill without their fans  or most commonly known as MANDIRIGMA, wouldnt be as successful as they are right now. Without their gasoline, Jamill wouldnt have the fame.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/S8poq8nRIRrWHjbAKrYzpiDfOzeexHsZZ7caJ6A03YKbwZAHfR51B_UVPmXjA_dy3b9oZNzZArmru_yhjt0WbHQ5I45r4lE6xXcVBhMMSuYt590UqpKKA3LTnsOs79pyyzYVlrwD\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BnbIEj1FilL/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=lly95b3h6dhu</span>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">But who are these fans? What is mandirigma?\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Mandirigma in english simply means warrior and a warrior is someone who fights along with other warriors to achieve a goal. These warriors, of course, work for their king.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Just like warriors, Jamills Mandirigmas are fighters. They make sure no one talks badly about their idol. They fight what they know is right. They treasure Jamill just like how warriors treasure their king.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Mandirigmas are also resilient. Remember when Jamill faced a controversy, their fans didnt leave them. They were always there protecting Jamill. Truth or not, they still stayed with them against all the bash. And slowly, they stood up again with their idol.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/4KEedVMw2geYHcHMGSOwSHCV1gadsn0PZV6Mfspdwf3vd6wpJNlrekwSNVo9Y6IeqO_Gyl9cFll3edGjqNhFSjoS5z0iOa6PHKV8XckhkP9Swf7yOnzSt5_hFHDDXxNeZanA0Vge\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BiW8KNNFErq/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=7mr0mdvyiagf</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Above all, mandirigmas should be commended with how supportive they are. Of course every fandom is and should be supportive but mandirigma is different.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">They are warriors. They protect and fight. They support Jamill without putting others down. They have their own kingdom with strong and resilient barrier no one could ever put down.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/hvX23cGf25oW_XeSNRG1JNRu2zSvccjx0EbRuadwWeCxX58eXVEbTkq5qFo7dzpHfACnjp4Now-4BIbhFU8P0YIw9_7GEO6s8m-AFfCqEoS6E1SRMAiMuY0CM7-SjL3_aZLk82uZ\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BkmvlF5lRMq/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=gw2ed9dtk668</span>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Again, what is mandirigma?\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Mandirigma is Jamills warrior. A warrior that is strong and resilient. A warrior that protects, loves and cares. A warrior that stays. Ahu!\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/CsJIMAKTkMa9ClIXQL29qT2dnaQobpcj6o0Sv-GmzvzlFu0V_cukqtJodND33UZSNY3GV3gaXhxNDqEsa47U_W2ROFSMyzs8DwEcrsD_83rtUWuF1oCnBTJ4wrtfb84tOTGrVLcq\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Image courtesy of Jamill https://www.instagram.com/p/BmQlAEYl4rD/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=qyagpu33px67</span></p>', 'Who are the people behind Jamill\'s success?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'who-are-the-people-behind-jamills-success', '', '', '2018-09-21 20:03:19', '2018-09-21 20:03:19', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=476', 0, 'post', '', 0),
