(479, 2, '2018-09-20 08:06:30', '2018-09-20 08:06:30', '<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c11\"></span><span class=\"c2\">Naging ganyan kasakit kase naging ganun kasaya,</span><span class=\"c1\"> if you have watched the trailer of NKNKK, these words might have engraved in your minds.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/m3bsiaGH9TBDfoO7D3KtK5vvsQvUJ1dg9sdeHjTUwdY2NXcgxD3E3dVuNQmz5EzjSfzhYDXpZUIqr1thghptBAIGiC6fEmu5zLBxgz_oMEoKjymf9BlJW08yVFyBJB5u9k64lhUj\" alt=\"C:\\Users\\neo\\Desktop\\alex\\Screenshot_2018-09-20-19-56-50.png\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Wilbros Films https://youtu.be/Yz5-DdsL480</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c11\">This most awaited</span><span class=\"c2\">hugot</span><span class=\"c1\">movie by Wilbros Films proves that moving on from a heartbreak is one of the hardest things to do. This movie of Fifth Solomons debut as a director and writer entails Jas (portrayed by Alex Gonzaga) and Migs (played by Vin Abrebica) who were deeply inlove yet fell short in their relationship.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/L-WU6e7Zj6sU3n4McA05v5RdBwobG0xX4yr5oPcqc4o_feTHRR5euYCsEx0r_KgWed9DW-TU-2f-3XT06CQpQE1frK2sKnOhf55-65erkr96p8ncFqwkJrSFtVwIUMe6gqmx16zA\" alt=\"C:\\Users\\neo\\AppData\\Local\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Temporary Internet Files\\Content.Word\\Screenshot_2018-09-20-20-10-59.png\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Wilbros Films https://youtu.be/Yz5-DdsL480</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c1\">In her hope to forget the pain caused by her ex-lover, Jas accompanied by her best friend (played by Jerald Napoles) went to search for a cure. This is where Rolex (played by (Candi Pangilinan) enters. It also stars Rufa Mae Quinto, Jayson Gainza, Loisa Andalio, Alora Sasam, Joj and Jai Agpangan, Ricci Chan, Juan Miguel Severo, Cai Cortez and Keiko Necesario.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/pNYYhqzdI8PZoCb8_OTsUT5UJz9M9cW-Wa8wl_op3BW6dXWMED1ttoz4M4_Xw7oGXUJtfMIUHlmHUQ0noY1OQaqn4h0RI3JISXSHjgGumGvdPkLdQuvL5ghSx32W3g9XogIABwDX\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Wilbros Films https://youtu.be/Yz5-DdsL480</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c1\">This movie circles a simple plot showing the different stages of moving on. It shows a unique and unpredictable way to forget.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c1\">It gives realistic and relatable emotions and not to forget, humor as it takes you to the beauty of Bataan. It is a story of a womans love that failed. It is a story of a broken heart that wants to be mended.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/IpVtH_msdRpRVNDT9Mr7keU1AgK7RR9y7EjO63nRMQHWGhqFKsOOUxVQLxljaYRNOfiaFsBC9WqmQNfh8jprLOoTsyvFWJE6SzaCfm6smk2VzKKahdJ19Gy3JyTbUpKk4eHDj8fT\" alt=\"C:\\Users\\neo\\Desktop\\alex\\Screenshot_2018-09-20-20-04-55.png\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Wilbros Films https://youtu.be/Yz5-DdsL480</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c11\">At some point in our lives, we already loved and lost and probably wanted to do everything to find a cure. As Candi said </span><span class=\"c2\">Dahil ang totoong na pagibig ay hindi basta bastang nakakalimutan</span><span class=\"c1\">, loving and forgetting are both hard to do. But in time, everything falls back to where it is supposed to be.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/KZwQmGGsAZvQk3sXlqaR0OWGqCwSHElYPFlrY2jMPx4jcS-4caWuYarltdy2hCwSiYQwifA-N8q09lYz6y5hDBoWtfeYlczeAKpjesaB2tcdRtQR4HXvAyOTdJU-pb3YTPhv2qZl\" alt=\"C:\\Users\\neo\\Desktop\\alex\\Screenshot_2018-09-20-20-03-18.png\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Wilbros Films https://youtu.be/Yz5-DdsL480</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c5\"><span class=\"c1\">Will this #HugotMovie give us the answer weve been waiting for? Watch Nakalimutan Ko Nang Kalimutan Ka, now showing in cinemas and find it out yourselves.</span></p>', 'Will Nakalimutan Ko Nang Kalimutan Ka Give Us the Cure for Broken Hearts?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'will-nakalimutan-ko-nang-kalimutan-ka-give-us-the-cure-for-broken-hearts', '', '', '2018-09-22 20:14:24', '2018-09-22 20:14:24', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=479', 0, 'post', '', 0),
