(482, 2, '2018-09-21 20:07:43', '2018-09-21 20:07:43', 'This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pia coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://page5.ph/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Page5ph', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-21 20:07:43', '2018-09-21 20:07:43', '', 2, 'http://page5.ph/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(483, 3, '2018-09-17 14:04:47', '2018-09-17 14:04:47', '<p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c9\">Kimpoy Feliciano is still taking the internet by storm and is proving that his fame is not going to fade anytime yet soon.</span></p>\r\n<p id=\"h.u5zaawut1ygr\" class=\"c7\"><strong><span class=\"c15\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #000000;\">Recently, he was just named as the Most Influential Male Social Media Personality in the University of Perpetual Help-Las Pinas Alta Media Icon Awards.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c9\">Feliciano who rose to fame because of his love advice and pick-up lines can also be remembered as a peace ambassador for social media in the I Am for Peace campaign of the Malacaang Palace back in 2012. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c9\">Up to this day, the internet personality continues to utilize his social media accounts to share positivity, good vibes, and should we even mention, his charm.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c2\"><span class=\"c9\">Kimpoy is expected to receive his award on October 5, 2018 during the awarding ceremony.</span></p>', 'Kimpoy is the Most Influential Male Online', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kimpoy-is-the-most-influential-male-online', '', '', '2018-09-22 20:11:52', '2018-09-22 20:11:52', '', 0, 'http://page5.ph/?p=483', 0, 'post', '', 0),
