(514, 3, '2018-09-23 20:41:40', '2018-09-23 20:41:40', 'This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pia coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://page5.ph/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Page5ph', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-23 20:41:40', '2018-09-23 20:41:40', '', 2, 'https://page5.ph/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(516, 3, '2018-09-24 09:49:29', '2018-09-24 09:49:29', '<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c9\">Its (almost) here! MAC Cosmetics has finally revealed its latest lipstick shade in collaboration with</span><span class=\"c8\">EatBulaga</span><span class=\"c1\">host and actress Maine Mendoza.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">The actress first announced her collaboration with MAC last January 19, 2018 in her Instagram account @mainedcm. It feels surreal to be chosen as one of the influencers and to be the first Filipina to have a lipstick collaboration with MAC, said Maine.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-439\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"619\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Maine Medoza https://www.instagram.com/p/BeHlMDEhJKw/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1lenlt4fner8t</span>\r\n\r\nDubbed as the @mainedcm shade, Maine opted for a matte finished muted peachy beige shade that would work well on a variety of skin tones. A universal nude lipstick that everyone can wear for any occasion.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-440\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image01.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"492\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-441\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"492\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Images courtesy of @maccosmeticsph https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn350U1HmbL/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=iny8d7f8ud3s</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">The lipstick comes in an exclusive customized kiss-print packaging made and signed by Maine herself.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-442\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"494\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c9\">Images courtesy of @maccosmeticsph</span><span class=\"c9 c10\"><a class=\"c15\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn34KNOHDVQ/?utm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3Ddey9ndxodrox&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1537559087175000\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn34KNOHDVQ/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=dey9ndxodrox</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c9\">As the first Filipina that MAC Cosmetics ever collaborated with, everyone couldnt be prouder. Few of those who gave their support are, of course</span><span class=\"c8\">hindi papahuli,</span><span class=\"c1\">the beauty vloggers.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-443\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image04.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"594\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Raiza Contawi</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Last September 17, an event with MAC cosmetics team and Maine Mendoza for #MaineForMac was attended by popular beauty gurus of Youtube. They are Say Tioco, Raiza Contawi, Baninay Bautista and Raf Juane. This event was in Say Tiocos latest vlog.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-444\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image05.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"612\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Raiza Contawi https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn1G3WYFpFb/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=zm4j6co06m3g</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-445\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/maine-image06.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"612\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Baninay Bautista https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn6N3iChqy9/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=2xn08kh70pje</span>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-446\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-20-21-00-48-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"490\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Say Tioco https://www.instagram.com/p/Bn28E5khock/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=fqowjccswum7</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Raiza Contawi also cant hide her excitement as she unboxed and gave her first impression on the product through a video on her youtube channel.</span></p>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-447\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-20-21-34-03-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" />\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Raiza Contawi https://youtu.be/9JG6U1jrdLo</span></p>\r\n<p id=\"h.gjdgxs\" class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Also, Raf Juane already has a challenge of wearing Mac Cosmetics for 8 hours in his channel. Of course, one of those products is Maines lipstick.</span><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-448\" src=\"http://page5.ph/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screenshot_2018-09-20-21-47-17-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of About Raf https://youtu.be/eJayaClpybQ</span></p>\r\n<p id=\"h.gjdgxs-1\" class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c9\">Everyone must have their hands itch with eagerness. The most awaited limited-edition lippie will be out on September 21 in Lazada, 22 in Megamall and 23 in all MAC stores nationwide! Whos excited?</span></p>', '#MaineForMac Attended By Beauty Vloggers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '438-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-24 09:49:29', '2018-09-24 09:49:29', '', 438, 'https://page5.ph/438-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(517, 3, '2018-09-24 10:42:24', '2018-09-24 10:42:24', '<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c5\">The night of September 23</span><span class=\"c2\">rd</span><span class=\"c0\">, the personalities of the digital community have again gathered in the E! Bloggers Ball 2018 for a night of glamour and elegance. It was attended by the countrys top social media influencers, bloggers, vloggers, Youtubers and celebrities.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/hsxmk4swj5c2I-JBQDIBvOOgtA9veuXps5HMZnopI_kv_pEIY9_Kk0OIMWyItMYRDcP2oTRFyhZWog_SE7EOK91g935GmRb8W0RuNoekvpeemzGdoi2l4nZ1RSzQDMl0dBm_N7-C\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of E! Philippines https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEnCl4n26E/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=yo08v78hbt4y</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Everyone made the night spectacular as the social media influencers came with their dashing and shining formal attires. It was like a Hollywood awards night.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/n-8tuR_Nsvpc79SJadGJztHNoqRGzG99eL78kWcCFCR45PetuE_mTVIvVGJa1aVWX3TBAWWhh-AFldQ1NtEE4xQ1WnLzwBzUTjBChYbA301xn5kask3VomWq8m0nRs_J5Ijr0ksf\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c5\">Image courtesy of E! Philippines </span><span class=\"c4\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEnt7Wn3BM/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=18gooa65f7q61</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/48HFz7Q1P-QdUa68dbZhYgz9xLBS4bT5felUZNL6EUcpF-kdW_DTW5jR8HUOGYR7JuRyHOdko1pXbTupMLIMrOt4GZGk2Hl9ONlBU24GdKcY0FAUF6AzrlQOqtCXFp3_RtpdecZe\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c5\">Image courtesy of Ronan Domingo </span><span class=\"c4\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEk9V8ls2Z/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=s5kssq4bjro7</span></span></p>\r\n<p c