bgFwxUhGiKQNELYfjmt0H9qdI-SjfPAjH7S7XsXL833ryhRvs4fKxCKxa9IzVG_eAfqg02CZm-p_w7egGEj8l6mwMqVQa_tpgVnw18HqM1gEY4xy0uZvgL_fgMtEPI\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c5\">Image courtesy of E! Philippines </span><span class=\"c4\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEotBuHh7x/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1gdx2h6153vuc</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/s48KQKk_fAc1eK5bDwQUIbFqJwpdKwW6ovnzaPQnWs8UsbN6KzEwOmeMeXYH064e5fYg0BmfPVwvCREHuGP-l8E3yDRz_m23NPwZe6MIRooeO-hQBXLx4Agg_pL9zZjA_eig91Sl\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of E! Philippines https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEndn1HQhS/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=fzd107muuxmj</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">The E! Bloggers Ball is an event to appreciate all the influencers efforts and hardworks. This night is theirs to enjoy. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/hLox00gtXWVXCpBGCDCg2S6MQRJOgi4KW5kE59vSDr3KRoYJEpzCLVhKxTLe9RU4Q6H-Ucag6xoUmuyDwc9gecOs7DlVbKHTmFK6TCHnMbbz86d5_ijnt79QqX5_7HSd-zYrGpu2\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c5\">Image courtesy of E! Philippines </span><span class=\"c4\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoEpB3DH96T/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=a2asfsumuxz</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/cMT-wAiG7kQ06ZpmxkALw2eT9zj8-mxQNGRghF8twM7gyzl3B4crVG9Vq7P4ImbrjW3xAV5NdH1FUJCh8zhiS2gXxHHxrFGo3-iiBUo3WhM4FkWQRGg9Pa0osxoFI2CLvIAceeky\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Mikki Galang</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c5\">While there are a lot of privileges an influencer has, he/she also started from scratch. The fruit that they are reaping right now is the product of their blood, sweat and tears. The fruit that they are reaping right now is what they deserve.</span></p>', 'E! Bloggers Ball: Influencers Night', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '502-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-09-24 10:42:24', '2018-09-24 10:42:24', '', 502, 'https://page5.ph/502-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(518, 3, '2018-09-25 09:00:54', '2018-09-25 01:00:54', '<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">As the issue on cosmetic animal testing continues, more and more people express their opinions via social media including beauty vlogger, Lou Sanchez.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">With more than 11,000 followers, she wrote on her twitter account that whats happening to the beauty industry is disappointing and irritating. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">Mahirap, nakakainis, nakaka-disappoint pero Ive decided, Ill do the Big Switch! #CrueltyFree #LittleStepsForTheAnimals</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/rewiiyxRGIz4owBqFALNsihb0qeAgyCOUasPE3arT6pxBQhmKm3b4mm_gb5L5XIvq8ciKiZCxxQJdiI91r6KCUau80-4Ucy9I15d1Mmi14T82G5jGc9cHYS-Ldi4F5yywaEmARG4\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">This then led her to decide of starting to switch with beauty brands that are genuinely cruelty-free.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">According to her, switching is actually a hard step to do, thats why she encouraged all her followers to stop buying brands or products that undergo the cruel process.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c1\">As she reinforces this advocate, she assured that there are still brands that are kind to animals.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c3\">In her thread, she even shared screenshots of her conversations of brands that proved their products are not tested on animals.<img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/l0Ek2A3avnEmL2B0-K2b4jJ8Hp-ZUv4zHWXzm0GXKJ7-YjS3FEGe-ysg5s0HKcw2pB-NNLwUK1ti-CaM9zIwmrKk_xowmoMsVk1U84oXNYUE1884oSsKtjg3a2V7KrUPqOCShIMF\" alt=\"\" /></p>', 'Lou Sanchez Expresses Disappointment On Animal Testing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lou-sanchez-expresses-disappointment-on-animal-testing', '', '', '2018-09-26 18:55:18', '2018-09-26 10:55:18', '', 0, 'https://page5.ph/?p=518', 0, 'post', '', 0),
