(534, 3, '2018-09-25 12:00:46', '2018-09-25 04:00:46', '<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Weve seen some of the most impressive gowns in the history of E!s red carpet as the E! Bloggers Ball celebrates their night of glamour and elegance. It was truly a very tough match of equally stunning ladies with their exquisite gowns.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">But among the beautiful attendees, there are a few who definitely stood out with their shining and shimmering dresses.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">We at Page 5 present to you our own Top 5 Best Dressed Female of the night.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><strong><span class=\"c1\">5. Alex Gonzaga</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/ziNReDKRjYFjoksx1LTr20ST3olT3AVrOhuSBNNya1MXkq2ByHIKH1LGOYeo3yw2eMCqPQh-bjs1WhpY2o7xgkREKua1l-zxDPTAjkrvn0fqNZEEOkcDSqoWi1AwP2MmMb6Hqiyg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of megastyleph https://www.instagram.com/p/BoGseSHhx9D/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=4iat0h5amp12</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Wearing her Rajo Laurel frock, Alex shone bright and striking. Her curves were on point looking like a perfect silhouette.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><strong><span class=\"c1\">4. Janica Nam</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/D02TEu56Ur4bYwBs5fodZtgSvmgywMHfraXBO7IRDVRvhQl_ge5plbi5kMeHdb3_FNKKbimb-xC5BkeFEq6p4p40VGUuzT6SkDzYTWCXsD4CeGOmFr5_OpHLkQD6YSIoqn3S3rgC\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of megastyleph https://www.instagram.com/p/BoGseSHhx9D/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=4iat0h5amp12</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Living the princess life, Janica entered the red carpet with her beaded Manny Halasan dress with her clean bun complementing her dazzling look.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><strong><span class=\"c1\">3. Michelle Dy</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/AHe7lA-ahV_I5Ii7Gkxq6zQF9AQdPRNioqKV0_heAMlzAjqd6NmQbELLtIL1KHDy6CkPlZqDWqOPuKC6zHWVcGCd5TsMmd2T4yizC_PSS4BFf1QkTF33bqmBjwrGJ5LZrlFecsDQ\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Michelle Dy https://www.instagram.com/p/BoF_kxqlCP2/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1v9yx6h96wyw5</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">A truly red carpet killer, Michelle left everyone in awe as she showed up with Karimadons creation. Despite the fact that it was her first time to attend the said big event, she gave no signs of red carpet frights. Her kind of flowy metallic gown and her smoky eyes gave us a breathtaking picture.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><strong><span class=\"c1\">2. Hannah Pangilinan</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/BSYDt60Kn6M-_jvSiW6dWImnDrzzHXU1kQoImmnZTwRivexErwQaBSaRFkkBFr_hwW2sl9lgUW_9OvYV1WkNYwaaRFcKC6TTgsiiDNwqs0P04rsdoSxse8AgPPbqO-PCOhZFOZMx\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Hannah Pangilinan https://www.instagram.com/p/BoGH9asHWzc/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=11v1kiz2y3w23</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">In terms of sexiness and appeal, we can say Hannah owned the game. Wearing her Patricia Santos Atelier gown, Hannah showed off her curves in the best way. With additional points for her nicely brushed back hair and popping clavicles!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><strong><span class=\"c1\">1. Angela Muoz</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/2g0636gBTGlGawCmg6jEOF9CO9kaoLAfpkKtwLhqX2XCFoRkzEbTegDXXy439dSKilEcgI-rKrekb1X130aPwASOLYJ5NMzzBGddsRb7Zr3VH4Jtbjn5xEs9yUecQVEYClRny5oz\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><s