(569, 3, '2018-09-28 20:53:04', '2018-09-28 12:53:04', '<div id=\"contents\">\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\"><strong>Hey, hey, hey pastel lovers!</strong> School has started about two months already and probably most of your school supplies have run out already. Dont worry because we have you covered! </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/FvofpeZf_eDZkyaQOqZk-hqij8mgjK_dNFPI1AJn_kYHQGDMy2vEmnzwfO1ln6aBLwsxnxVaD7cImZ5xNM043i8epYgJpS4DqxxxnM7dAsVtal1yjpyz2tf7eHBj6UATIyPs-yeC\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"c2\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of National Bookstore</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">If you are a fan of pastel items and cute supplies and accessories, youll surely love the <strong>Janina x NBS</strong> collaboration. This special collaboration of NBS with beauty and lifestyle vlogger Janina features a variety of school supplies including tote bags, make up pouches, highlighters, notebooks and stickers. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/0Mi7xeRVRQMho4JclssyBPnRupuMA9A-7D-86UsExmPujzenUuBvPsVYG4RezDgY7PcxzlYk2TFj1G0_h-ibMChwUU8V3WQzZqh6OuZ4vm5UztdYFIvB2V7n0BfovQ_4i7j8JP-W\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"c4\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of National Bookstore</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">The items colors are pastel and very bright. Even the notebooks have cute and inspiring quotes personally made by the maker herself. If you are an avid subscriber of Janina, youd probably say the designs are very like her; bright and inspiring.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/8sKLZOF0pJA3xZD36LilH8zVCVAl1mRCYvNpR1UV83Ufa3jGkgquPqVbGsJTh2F93GQdL9VLQPiqQp3Egy5CIzkeFAUxIyxv4WzogZna4Fjd0w3ZLICQ-JXWaWwhWD2SgSo38dkg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/LRkZjzflDS_06pBzN9cNo8bqlEVk5-KmrbFbOFMyXVvgnh_yIff0EuUaEdkwXttcHPceS0rOmEx3v9lR9k59e6FvPBEecbH-052MB77IerlKXNg5TYjBmmxfN4pBiaBu_qp0tcR3\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"c4\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Images courtesy of Janina Vela https://www.instagram.com/p/BlVaz75Fu1d/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1jyzhvdmamzmh</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Lets check out her collection!</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">With just Php 59, you can have these cute spiral notebooks in different pastel colors.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/wwD3h1EOVXMSnfRcczg1vactWyhTDFZ4n32SNaNbRNTk810Tfzb3XvBB0b19mZOvabHhQ7OjsD5oBkalaJvk5--N9aAx61Q5FhkKRfSfL4xz01SIlAkVQ0h-m1JVZsUWKWN2C7k3\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"c4\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of National Bookstore</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">If you are a little extra with your notes, you can these journals in different sizes and designs starting at Php299.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/5vxKyFtIwv1YPV6MrFlzaxPO_Cu9-VI3FehwteA_5eqxeH24ap96rnxJ0YMgYEu5-PF1hIzczlvjsyqPWoM22VIyKoJSZPDnIMrvaAPFIVWtIOyzqYNuPLItf52mylyUwebnvjhf\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"c4\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of National Bookstore https://www.instagram.com/p/Blo3iYMAiAB/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=136lcnr4eqpz</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Want to have something pretty to keep your make up tools? For Php 249 you can get this make up pouch. If you want to organize your pens, pencils and writing gears, get this pencil case for as low as Php 199.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/CS3bsOhYuL8py013