(592, 3, '2018-09-30 14:13:30', '2018-09-30 06:13:30', '<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Its the time of the year again! The much awaited <strong>ABC-CBN Ball 2018</strong> lit with glitz and glamour as more than 600 celebrities wowed the red carpet with their equally unique and alluring frocks and suits. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Aside from the stunning outfits, these celebrities also had pinned blue ribbons that symbolize their support for the Bantay Bata 163 campaign to help create awareness and show support for abused children. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">The tagline #ShareTheLove, ABS-CBN Ball aims to draw attention to the emotional healing of abused children and to raise funds for the launching of the Bantay Bata 163 childrens Village in Norzagaray, Bulacan which will serve as their safe haven.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">Among the sea of dazzling celebrities, few of our favorite social media influencers also slayed the night! Here are the countrys most renowned influencers in their glitziest looks. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><strong><span class=\"c0\">Erwan Heussaff </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/4s2U8f70_rCa8BrqU-4K-2EMwOFROhVQ5Gpj3qz-g23HCpbsjaKcWulFUE53QP2tElre6_to553hhugKiX_AqlefvnHccsBJ455LFVf7PU6NTYQWc8Y8uc_0MxmhGdQS0v_6g18c\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c3\" style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">Image courtesy of Metro Society Ph </span><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c5\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.instagram.com/p/BoT9lWpgq8A/?utm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3Dkvhfjagx8r7&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1538289405857000\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoT9lWpgq8A/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=kvhfjagx8r7</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c0\">A prince from a story book, Erwan dazzled in his suit with a bonus of a stunning date.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><strong><span class=\"c0\">AC Bonifacio</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/04gIMoDCM9nDvpaZT3XkTxSSrYvEHV328EtgB9HeYaoP7yeGh4tox8LZga3MFgddISMwVml1lpAcvlT5ao81Cgp87rlmi9TkuxcLmh2JPCrP4-pNyKrIOQRIzb2io5DRtvesIxuu\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c3\">Image courtesy of GMO Entertainment </span><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c5\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.instagram.com/p/BoTwwfHnU9C/?utm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D118xmz8lbzwjs&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1538289405857000\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoTwwfHnU9C/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=118xmz8lbzwjs</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c3\">The dancing princess Ac is looking sweet and pretty in her gown.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><strong><span class=\"c0\">Alexa Ilacad</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Xe-BCHa-0YcbXdZE42v6zmDUeoD04iHdjAglqhQoN6iIQhyH1U1FtH3RBEyde0EAx_YO6SDOhKF-GWu3iT8Vx1A-jnQAbnqt4SkqEOX2psAm5iD_UYOU47kzJXyzP6SKKvmZ1oCh\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt;\"><span class=\"c3\">Image courtesy of The Qrwon Ph </span><span class=\"c2\"><a class=\"c5\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.instagram.com/p/BoTsu-tH5fe/?utm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3Dqkqzfw5rrymy&amp;sa=D&amp;ust=1538289405858000\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BoTsu-tH5fe/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=qkqzfw5rrymy</a></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><span class=\"c3\">Alexa is a sweetheart of the night in her Grecian dress. Not to forget her mermaid-esque blonde strands hair. </span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><strong><span class=\"c0\">Maris Racal</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"c1\"><img title=\"\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/WvTHSPEv7SVD_rMWA4-b4NT-5czp2G2cjglIvm4b9ZviAjRcBGdtoKGuXkFZI73gpTfXXchmpMdUb