(602, 3, '2018-10-01 17:18:16', '2018-10-01 09:18:16', '<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">The efforts and dedication of TV and Real-life couple Ja Mill and Dance group LiveLoveParty truly paid off as they reached another milestone in their Youtube careers.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">They are the latest to receive the Gold Creator Award, a recognition that is given to Youtube content creators who reached 1 million subscribers in their respective channels while maintaining a good standing of Youtubes Community Guidelines and Terms of Services.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Winning the hearts of young Filipinos by their charming and lighthearted videos, the young couple Jayzam Trinidad and Camille Manabat (Ja Mill) managed to grow their channel.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">While LiveLoveParty proves that their tutorial videos are unique and relatable to everyone especially to those who are looking for fitness routines but considers fun and entertainment at the same time.\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"c0\">Google Philippines Country Marketing Manager Gabby Roxas expressed pride with the 2 local channels.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"c3\">Were proud to present the Gold Creator Award to LiveLoveParty.TV and Ja Mill. Their passion, talent, and wit are a great inspiration for the growing Filipino YouTube community, </span><span class=\"c1\">said Roxas.\r\n\r\nJa Mill and LiveLoveParty joins the roster of Michelle Dy, Lloyd Cadena, Wil Dasovich, and Alex Gonzaga, among others.</span></p>', 'Gold Play Button Awarded to 2 more Filipino Youtube Channels', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gold-play-button-awarded-to-2-more-filipino-youtube-channels', '', '', '2018-10-01 17:18:16', '2018-10-01 09:18:16', '', 0, 'https://page5.ph/?p=602', 0, 'post', '', 0),
